highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 884 days straight.
“Pé na Rua - Ao Vivo” by Mari Fernandez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #121.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #12.
“Vai Cair Água - Ao Vivo” by Diego & Arnaldo and Zé Neto & Cristiano is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 94 spots at #80.
